{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":667,"text":"I'm a blogger, a filmmaker and a butcher,"},{"time":3866,"text":"and I'll explain how\nthese identities come together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":7068,"text":"It started four years ago,"},{"time":8764,"text":"when a friend and I opened\nour first Ramadan fast"},{"time":11420,"text":"at one of the busiest mosques\nin New York City."},{"time":14045,"text":"Crowds of men with beards and skullcaps\nwere swarming the streets."},{"time":17943,"text":"It was an FBI agent's wet dream.\n(Laughter)"},{"time":21548,"text":"But being a part of this community,\nwe knew how welcoming this space was."},{"time":25046,"text":"For years, I'd seen photos \nof this space being documented"},{"time":28363,"text":"as a lifeless and cold monolith,"},{"time":30470,"text":"much like the stereotypical image\npainted of the American Muslim experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34181,"text":"Frustrated by this myopic view,"},{"time":36474,"text":"my friend and I had this crazy idea:"},{"time":38876,"text":"Let's break our fast\nat a different mosque in a different state"},{"time":41877,"text":"each night of Ramadan"},{"time":43302,"text":"and share those stories on a blog."},{"time":45454,"text":"We called it \"30 Mosques in 30 Days,\""},{"time":47734,"text":"and we drove to all the 50 states"},{"time":49540,"text":"and shared stories from over 100\nvastly different Muslim communities,"},{"time":52905,"text":"ranging from the Cambodian refugees\nin the L.A. projects"},{"time":56234,"text":"to the black Sufis living\nin the woods of South Carolina."},{"time":59426,"text":"What emerged was a beautiful\nand complicated portrait of America."},{"time":62795,"text":"The media coverage\nforced local journalists"},{"time":64820,"text":"to revisit their Muslim communities,"},{"time":66557,"text":"but what was really exciting\nwas seeing people from around the world"},{"time":70177,"text":"being inspired to take\ntheir own 30-mosque journey."},{"time":73184,"text":"There were even these two NFL athletes"},{"time":75001,"text":"who took a sabbatical\nfrom the league to do so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77277,"text":"And as 30 Mosques\nwas blossoming around the world,"},{"time":80614,"text":"I was actually stuck in Pakistan\nworking on a film."},{"time":83273,"text":"My codirector, Omar, and I were at \na breaking point with many of our friends"},{"time":86894,"text":"on how to position the film."},{"time":88559,"text":"The movie is called \"These Birds Walk,\""},{"time":90646,"text":"and it is about wayward street kids"},{"time":92406,"text":"who are struggling to find\nsome semblance of family."},{"time":95242,"text":"We focus on the complexities\nof youth and family discord,"},{"time":98710,"text":"but our friends kept on nudging us\nto comment on drones and target killings"},{"time":102495,"text":"to make the film \"more relevant,\""},{"time":105304,"text":"essentially reducing these people\nwho have entrusted us with their stories"},{"time":108810,"text":"into sociopolitical symbols."},{"time":110777,"text":"Of course, we didn't listen to them,"},{"time":112553,"text":"and instead, we championed\nthe tender gestures of love"},{"time":115973,"text":"and headlong flashes of youth."},{"time":118295,"text":"The agenda behind our cinematic \nimmersion was only empathy,"},{"time":121374,"text":"an emotion that's largely \ndeficient from films"},{"time":123958,"text":"that come from our region of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127233,"text":"And as \"These Birds Walk\" played at film \nfestivals and theaters internationally,"},{"time":131460,"text":"I finally had my feet\nplanted at home in New York,"},{"time":133943,"text":"and with all the extra time\nand still no real money,"},{"time":137505,"text":"my wife tasked me to cook more for us."},{"time":141190,"text":"And whenever I'd go to the local butcher\nto purchase some halal meat,"},{"time":144577,"text":"something felt off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145946,"text":"For those that don't know,\nhalal is a term used for meat"},{"time":149313,"text":"that is raised and slaughtered humanely\nfollowing very strict Islamic guidelines."},{"time":153855,"text":"Unfortunately, the majority\nof halal meat in America"},{"time":157209,"text":"doesn't rise to the standard\nthat my faith calls for."},{"time":160151,"text":"The more I learned\nabout these unethical practices,"},{"time":162852,"text":"the more violated I felt,"},{"time":164900,"text":"particularly because businesses\nfrom my own community"},{"time":168092,"text":"were the ones taking advantage\nof my orthodoxy."},{"time":171211,"text":"So, with emotions running high,\nand absolutely no experience in butchery,"},{"time":175225,"text":"some friends and I opened a meat store"},{"time":177474,"text":"in the heart of the\nEast Village fashion district."},{"time":180034,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":181394,"text":"We call it Honest Chops,"},{"time":183234,"text":"and we're reclaiming halal by sourcing\norganic, humanely raised animals,"},{"time":186947,"text":"and by making it accessible and affordable\nto working-class families."},{"time":190668,"text":"There's really nothing like it in America."},{"time":192817,"text":"The unbelievable part is actually\nthat 90 percent of our in-store customers"},{"time":196939,"text":"are not even Muslim."},{"time":198479,"text":"For many, it is their first time \ninteracting with Islam"},{"time":201206,"text":"on such an intimate level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203601,"text":"So all these disparate projects --\n(Laughter) --"},{"time":208347,"text":"are the result of a restlessness."},{"time":210522,"text":"They are a visceral response\nto the businesses and curators"},{"time":214106,"text":"who work hard to oversimplify\nmy beliefs and my community,"},{"time":217625,"text":"and the only way to beat their machine\nis to play by different rules."},{"time":221790,"text":"We must fight with an inventive approach."},{"time":223976,"text":"With the trust, with the access,\nwith the love that only we can bring,"},{"time":228317,"text":"we must unapologetically\nreclaim our beliefs"},{"time":230777,"text":"in every moving image,\nin every cut of meat,"},{"time":233419,"text":"because if we whitewash our stories\nfor the sake of mass appeal,"},{"time":237565,"text":"not only will we fail,"},{"time":239074,"text":"but we will be trumped by those\nwith more money and more resources"},{"time":242401,"text":"to tell our stories."},{"time":244211,"text":"But the call for creative courage\nis not for novelty or relevance."},{"time":248914,"text":"It is simply because our communities\nare so damn unique and so damn beautiful."},{"time":253767,"text":"They demand us to find uncompromising ways\nto be acknowledged and respected."},{"time":260603,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":262358,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}